{"tid":2505634,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係反送中嘅話大快活應該一早全線收曬皮","createTime":"2021-04-26T17:58:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T18:18:34.000Z","uid":330227,"like":8,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a899b217b4e96c7e8a15c8fe3a5980dbdce0f28a","tid":2505634,"uid":330227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T17:58:30.000Z","msg":"明明以前都好地地 呢幾年啲食物嘅質素差曬<br />\n得返個雞胸飯入得下口<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明明朝早唔係冇客 但係塊多士永遠都係凍嘅<br />\n連最重要嗰杯奶茶都用埋曬啲下欄淡奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/unexpected.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n晏晝同夜晚嗰啲小菜簡直係垃圾<br />\n又少料 又多油多鹽<br />\n個焗豬又乾又酸 不知所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老老實實如果唔係之前社會運動大家唔想食老麥/大家樂<br />\n又唔知食咩好嘅話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大快活應該一早因為疫情全線收皮 <br />\n好似atv咁樣成為歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac6083f42082178cb847ca1997444c807a6a370e","tid":2505634,"uid":330227,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T18:00:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好心大快活高層搞搞佢<br />\n好撚難食啊屌<br />\n請埋班啊嬸送飯有撚用咩"},{"pid":"5b0ce06ee4eebc1b46825964bd2010b401dc0e04","tid":2505634,"uid":192732,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T18:02:50.000Z","msg":"晏晝同夜晚嗰啲小菜簡直係垃圾<br />\n又少料 又多油多鹽<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n邊忽多油多鹽<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前食佢個口水雞 仲淡過人地啲白切雞 <br />\n<br />\n仲要骨多過肉"},{"pid":"b0c1850570180b5f3a7abcea4e7533ba36d84d53","tid":2505634,"uid":330227,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T18:03:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n估唔到咁多人中意食大快活<br />\n一分鐘已經五個負皮<br />\n<br />\n一人一個講大快活好味餸菜"},{"pid":"77e3fb44fc72f395864582149c4223199c690fc6","tid":2505634,"uid":81687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T18:04:14.000Z","msg":"焗豬真係酸到仆街"},{"pid":"7024521d8d7f780eca89de23c1d45b6e5da8ca07","tid":2505634,"uid":12480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T18:05:00.000Z","msg":"真 啲款冇新意都算 仲要越黎越垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d03f7e94888aab89b81476244f59625ff805e588","tid":2505634,"uid":330227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b0ce06ee4eebc1b46825964bd2010b401dc0e04","tid":2505634,"uid":192732,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T18:02:50.000Z","msg":"晏晝同夜晚嗰啲小菜簡直係垃圾<br />\n又少料 又多油多鹽<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n邊忽多油多鹽<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前食佢個口水雞 仲淡過人地啲白切雞 <br />\n<br />\n仲要骨多過肉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T18:05:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前食佢沙薑雞鹹撚到仆街"},{"pid":"e88e8e95706c7c234d7caddd796e21f1527bb398","tid":2505634,"uid":92299,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T18:05:11.000Z","msg":"大家樂先難食過屎喎, 佢個一哥焗豬塊豬排好似係地下磨過幾廿次先拎去焗咁, 已經冇食5, 6年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw大家樂高層我屌你老母, 唔該叫